{"tid":2309153,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"回應黃之鋒等人被判刑 陸委會批評是秋後算帳 民進黨:中共與港府應受最嚴厲譴責","createTime":"2020-12-02T10:52:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-02T12:02:18.000Z","uid":240362,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"49b1c13a4aedc1fdbd8e5c756ed2eb65e181f0d5","tid":2309153,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T10:52:35.000Z","msg":"前香港眾志的黃之鋒、林朗彥及周庭涉及去年6月21日的包圍警察總部案判刑，3人被判即時入獄。<br />\n<br />\n在台北，陸委會深表關切及遺憾，批評有關方面非但未能善盡政府保障人民權利的責任，反而不斷秋後算帳、清除異己，擠壓社會民主自由空間，破壞香港的繁榮穩定。<br />\n<br />\n陸委會呼籲相關方面應落實保障港人的自由與權利，確實遵守對國際社會及人民的承諾，勿再恃強凌弱、打壓人民，否則終被唾棄。<br />\n<br />\n民進黨表示，中共與港府以國家安全為理由，製造政治恐怖、殺雞儆猴，徹底背離一國兩制承諾，摧毀香港自治與民主自由，應受最嚴厲譴責。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1563225-20201202.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1563225-20201202.htm&d=u42ujRIT%2FE%2FeodHrCKN%2BOQexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=77260567\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1563225-20201202.htm&h=47c967c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1563225-20201202.htm</a>"},{"pid":"e528340fbc7aedb1d94dd46473e5a8cddba2dbe8","tid":2309153,"uid":371558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T11:07:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5672969b01ab16fb5b36d124b809a3966b852b4e","tid":2309153,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T11:44:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77738ecd0ef87dd20fc07cf89ffb879103413167","tid":2309153,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T11:45:09.000Z","msg":"引用的推文得2K, 要幫手回覆<br />\n最簡單就係覆<br />\n#StandWithHK<br />\n#AgnesChow<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/chowtingagnes/status/1334038156035821570\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fchowtingagnes%2Fs